1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:42,580 --> 00:01:44,860
It's my first time
dressing this formally.

4
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:46,180
Feels a bit unusual.

5
00:01:46,666 --> 00:01:48,622
You'll get used to it after a few times.

6
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,500
Will you come with me?

7
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:52,300
I won't.

8
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:54,780
It's Author Night, not Editor Night.

9
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,860
You used to go before.

10
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:00,340
You went with He Han.

11
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:06,820
Hello.

12
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:09,220
Do you have any bow ties I can try?

13
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:11,500
This tie feels a bit off.

14
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:17,600
Do you have other colors?

15
00:02:20,940 --> 00:02:21,740
Do you think

16
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:23,500
standing next to me

17
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,900
isn't as impressive

18
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,300
as standing next to He Han?

19
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:27,820
Of course not.

20
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:29,460
Someone sloppy,

21
00:02:30,066 --> 00:02:31,288
always late or leaving early,

22
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:32,300
face-blind,

23
00:02:32,977 --> 00:02:35,066
unwilling to handle
basic social interactions,

24
00:02:35,977 --> 00:02:37,460
and a walking bundle of trouble

25
00:02:37,580 --> 00:02:39,740
needs a person by his side
to smooth things over.

26
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:45,980
So if I were like He Han,

27
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:47,540
full of flaws,

28
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:48,780
you'd go with me?

29
00:02:50,140 --> 00:02:51,300
You can't put it that way.

30
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:54,780
Please come.

31
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,860
For the sake of me
always submitting on time

32
00:02:58,340 --> 00:02:59,940
and not causing trouble,

33
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:02,244
you wouldn't want
me to turn into He Han,

34
00:03:02,488 --> 00:03:03,620
a mess of issues, right?

35
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:07,620
This looks good.

36
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:11,340
Sir.

37
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:11,980
Hey.

38
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:13,260
Remember to pay.

39
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,620
Boss, four buns.

40
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:20,220
(Mengtong Internet Cafe)

41
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,140
- I'm back.
- Alright.

42
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:21,780
You're back.

43
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,133
What's with all those bags?

44
00:03:24,155 --> 00:03:25,010
Bought these for me?

45
00:03:25,010 --> 00:03:26,860
Don't I need formal wear
for Author Night?

46
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:27,900
Let me see.

47
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:30,740
This looks high-end.

48
00:03:31,222 --> 00:03:32,533
Must've cost quite a bit.

49
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:34,420
I don't know.
Ms. Lin bought them for me.

50
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,066
By the way, this year at Author Night,

51
00:03:36,070 --> 00:03:37,710
I should be
the New Rising Author of the Year.

52
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:39,180
Make sure you watch the livestream.

53
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:40,820
Of course, we'll watch.

54
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:42,780
And this, I brought it
specially for you guys.

55
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,666
Remember to eat it tonight.
I'm heading back.

56
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:46,180
You're not eating?

57
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:46,900
Not joining us?

58
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:48,460
I already ate.

59
00:03:48,511 --> 00:03:49,955
I still need to work on my manuscript.

60
00:03:50,860 --> 00:03:51,540
Just leave him.

61
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:52,500
Can't you tell?

62
00:03:52,711 --> 00:03:54,511
He brought it just to show off to us.

63
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:55,380
Let's eat.

64
00:03:56,220 --> 00:03:56,900
I'm not eating.

65
00:03:59,533 --> 00:04:00,780
Why aren't you eating either?

66
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:04,540
I'll eat.

67
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:19,060
Why are you dressed so formally today?

68
00:04:20,420 --> 00:04:21,740
Author Night is coming up.

69
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:23,380
I agreed to go with Gu Yan.

70
00:04:24,088 --> 00:04:26,555
It's been a while since I
attended something like this.

71
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:29,220
I wanted to try on
outfits and see what works.

72
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:31,460
What is he wearing?

73
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:33,500
I had a suit made for him.

74
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,100
Finally, someone presentable.

75
00:04:37,711 --> 00:04:39,088
What do you think of this one?

76
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:42,100
It looks nice.

77
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:45,940
But I think your white one looks better.

78
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:47,940
That one.

79
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:53,300
Wait.

80
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:56,420
Are you okay?

81
00:05:11,377 --> 00:05:12,100
No, that won't work.

82
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:12,780
Why not?

83
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:17,622
I've worn it before.

84
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:18,740
So what?

85
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:20,340
Celebrities nowadays

86
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,940
even rewear clothes from ten years ago.

87
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:23,820
Forget it.

88
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:25,380
He Han gave me that one.

89
00:05:26,980 --> 00:05:27,733
Is he going, too?

90
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:29,300
Not sure.

91
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,100
What time is it?

92
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,244
Why aren't you leaving yet?

93
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:43,820
You've waited so long

94
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:46,500
for this dinner,
and now that it's finally here,

95
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,777
you're not in a hurry anymore?

96
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:49,180
He said he'd be half an hour late.

97
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:51,644
He's taking his wife back
to her parents' place first.

98
00:05:51,666 --> 00:05:52,866
You're not upset?

99
00:05:55,620 --> 00:05:56,820
What would being upset change?

100
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,180
When I met him,

101
00:05:58,180 --> 00:05:59,180
he was already married.

102
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:00,180
He never hid it.

103
00:06:00,555 --> 00:06:01,820
I can't stop him from dealing with

104
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:02,660
his family matters.

105
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:05,060
So you still hope

106
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,460
he has a happy family

107
00:06:06,580 --> 00:06:07,700
and a complete life?

108
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,660
In a way, yes.

109
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:14,340
I really can't understand

110
00:06:15,177 --> 00:06:16,488
this situation between you two.

111
00:06:26,660 --> 00:06:27,460
I like him,

112
00:06:29,711 --> 00:06:32,022
but I've said I don't want
to ruin his family.

113
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:35,100
I don't want to become Mrs. Bei.

114
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:46,955
See you.

115
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,644
Will Lawyer Bei be picking you up?

116
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:54,820
Who else?

117
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:06,820
May I ask who you are?

118
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:11,860
You're Lin Zhanqiao?

119
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:14,380
What do you want?

120
00:07:14,822 --> 00:07:15,940
Zhangzhu is your assistant?

121
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:17,180
Answer my question first.

122
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,100
What do you want?

123
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,020
Where's Zhangzhu?

124
00:07:19,020 --> 00:07:19,940
She's not here.

125
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:22,940
Fine.

126
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:24,911
Then, I'll tell you directly.

127
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:27,580
Have you been watching
too many short videos

128
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:30,260
about those tricks
of handling divorced men?

129
00:07:30,377 --> 00:07:32,100
You think you've got
Zhangzhu under control,

130
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:33,911
and then you can drive
a wedge between Cai and me?

131
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:36,020
He may be muddled, but I'm not.

132
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:37,260
Go ahead.

133
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:38,620
Tell me what you want.

134
00:07:38,755 --> 00:07:39,733
You won't get the person.

135
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:40,340
As for money,

136
00:07:41,177 --> 00:07:42,177
name your price.

137
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:43,620
Go on.

138
00:07:45,060 --> 00:07:46,400
I don't know when

139
00:07:46,466 --> 00:07:47,660
or under what circumstances

140
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:49,100
you met Cai and Zhangzhu,

141
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:50,900
but I'm telling you, this is childish.

142
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:52,220
Look at this.

143
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:54,340
Cai and I are
getting married in a few days.

144
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:56,930
Why are you stopping
Zhangzhu from coming?

145
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:57,980
That's enough. Stop talking.

146
00:07:57,980 --> 00:07:58,660
I understand now.

147
00:07:59,177 --> 00:07:59,940
You should be glad

148
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,530
I have no interest in
either Cai or his daughter.

149
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:03,400
I'm going on a date with my boyfriend.

150
00:08:04,066 --> 00:08:05,400
You said it yourself just now.

151
00:08:05,444 --> 00:08:07,460
You have another boyfriend.
I'm going to tell Cai.

152
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:09,300
Don't pull me. My clothes are expensive.

153
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,755
If you tear them, Cai will pay.

154
00:08:13,288 --> 00:08:14,850
Don't touch me with your silicone pads.

155
00:08:14,888 --> 00:08:16,311
These are real. You're insulting me.

156
00:08:16,940 --> 00:08:17,860
Cai, listen,

157
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:19,860
Lin Zhanqiao just said
she has a boyfriend.

158
00:08:19,860 --> 00:08:21,140
You've both been fooled.

159
00:08:21,666 --> 00:08:23,088
Can you stop making a scene?

160
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:25,820
She's not my girlfriend at all.

161
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:28,500
I've barely even spoken to her.

162
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:29,180
I don't care.

163
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:33,420
Where are you?

164
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:34,666
Downstairs at her place.

165
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:36,740
Fine, wait there.

166
00:08:41,180 --> 00:08:41,660
Doctor,

167
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:43,140
well...

168
00:08:43,955 --> 00:08:45,311
I have something urgent.

169
00:08:45,420 --> 00:08:46,533
I need to leave first.

170
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,022
How much longer will this take?

171
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:50,977
We haven't done the left side yet.
There are a few more shots on the right.

172
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:54,140
Then finish the right side.

173
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:55,380
As for the left,

174
00:08:55,577 --> 00:08:56,888
I'll do it another day.

175
00:08:56,977 --> 00:08:59,177
Then let's schedule
another appointment tomorrow.

176
00:08:59,500 --> 00:08:59,900
Okay.

177
00:09:02,466 --> 00:09:03,933
If it weren't for the wedding,

178
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:05,660
I wouldn't go through this.

179
00:09:07,755 --> 00:09:09,822
Doctor, didn't you say it wouldn't hurt?

180
00:09:17,377 --> 00:09:19,155
I've never seen
a woman as shameless as you.

181
00:09:19,177 --> 00:09:20,970
And I've never seen a woman
as foolish as you.

182
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:21,380
Move.

183
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:22,900
Zhou Mei.

184
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,020
What did you just call her?

185
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:30,420
Do you need any help?

186
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:31,900
It's fine.

187
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:33,540
Just pre-wedding nerves.

188
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:35,340
You're not Lin Zhanqiao?

189
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:36,700
I never said I was.

190
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,660
You're the one who insisted I was.

191
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:39,140
Well...

192
00:09:39,533 --> 00:09:40,822
If you're not Lin Zhanqiao,

193
00:09:40,866 --> 00:09:42,610
the one next to you in the photo
must be her.

194
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:43,688
So where is Lin Zhanqiao?

195
00:09:43,700 --> 00:09:44,740
I need to find her.

196
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:46,340
Are you obsessed?

197
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,300
She's not home.

198
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:49,355
What do you want?

199
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,540
Call Cai Dezhang
and have him come pick you up.

200
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:53,860
You're not Lin Zhanqiao.

201
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:55,140
How do you know Cai Dezhang?

202
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:56,700
Who says only Lin Zhanqiao

203
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:57,740
can know Cai Dezhang?

204
00:09:58,088 --> 00:09:59,420
Please don't come any closer.

205
00:09:59,540 --> 00:10:00,660
You might get hit by a car.

206
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:03,980
Hello, Mr. Cai?

207
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:07,260
Could you come over for a moment?

208
00:10:07,860 --> 00:10:08,340
Thank you.

209
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:11,900
Let's go.

210
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:13,380
Wait a bit.

211
00:10:13,644 --> 00:10:14,822
Let's wait for him to arrive.

212
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:17,900
I won't let her off.

213
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:18,700
I will find her.

214
00:10:21,222 --> 00:10:23,266
You're worried
she'll go after Lin Zhanqiao?

215
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:28,580
Looks like our dinner
will be delayed again.

216
00:10:29,977 --> 00:10:32,288
Spending another half hour
with you isn't so bad.

217
00:10:33,888 --> 00:10:35,955
What time will you
pick your wife up tonight?

218
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:37,700
10 PM.

219
00:10:38,088 --> 00:10:39,260
I'll let you go on time.

220
00:10:48,666 --> 00:10:51,422
(The Road of Investment Banking)
(It was a rectangular office table,)

221
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:53,060
(seating about ten people.)

222
00:10:53,700 --> 00:10:54,700
(On it were piled)

223
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:56,780
(large black A4 folders,)

224
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:58,580
(stack after stack,)

225
00:10:58,580 --> 00:10:59,820
(materials from the Fa Group,)

226
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:02,380
(along with countless
scattered paper clips.)

227
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:05,100
(Chai Hu's unusual behavior)

228
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:07,820
(made Wang Muxue
pause what she was doing.)

229
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:10,740
Hello, Zhangzhu.

230
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:11,540
Ms. Lin,

231
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:14,020
Dingqi Platform just sent

232
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:15,460
fifty promising new authors

233
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:17,220
based on their big data analysis.

234
00:11:17,860 --> 00:11:18,700
On my end,

235
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,740
I quickly reviewed their genres,

236
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:22,980
reader feedback, and writing style,

237
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,780
and I've shortlisted twenty.

238
00:11:24,844 --> 00:11:26,180
I've already synced it to you.

239
00:11:26,977 --> 00:11:28,866
You're still at the office working late?

240
00:11:35,140 --> 00:11:36,620
Yes, I plan to go through

241
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:38,500
more of their other works,

242
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:40,820
then I'll head back.

243
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:43,660
Have you eaten?

244
00:11:43,660 --> 00:11:44,620
Want me to save you some?

245
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:45,700
No, I've eaten.

246
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:49,540
I just ordered
some takeout at the office.

247
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:51,060
Alright then, bye.

248
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,355
(Generally speaking...)

249
00:11:58,780 --> 00:11:59,500
Mr. He Han,

250
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:02,060
you see,

251
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:04,266
if Ms. Lin knew I was here eating

252
00:12:04,288 --> 00:12:06,500
while you're helping me review novels,

253
00:12:06,844 --> 00:12:07,955
would she be upset?

254
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:12,380
She'd pretend to be upset,

255
00:12:12,711 --> 00:12:14,400
but she'd actually be quite pleased.

256
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:20,580
Mr. He Han, I...

257
00:12:20,711 --> 00:12:22,140
I'm done eating, so I'll leave first.

258
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:23,020
Okay.

259
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:24,780
Be careful on your way.

260
00:12:24,844 --> 00:12:25,822
We'll continue tomorrow.

261
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:26,260
Alright.

262
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:46,420
Hello,

263
00:12:46,844 --> 00:12:48,060
Guiyuan Fields Nursing Home.

264
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:49,460
Yes.

265
00:12:50,180 --> 00:12:51,180
I'd like to ask,

266
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:53,740
is there an elderly man named He Wei

267
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:54,860
who checked in there?

268
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:57,020
He Wei?

269
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:58,860
Yes, Wei as in doing as one pleases.

270
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:00,300
Let me check.

271
00:13:01,244 --> 00:13:01,980
Yes, there is.

272
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:02,980
And you are?

273
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:04,540
I'm the son of his friend.

274
00:13:05,740 --> 00:13:06,860
He checked in today.

275
00:13:07,288 --> 00:13:08,760
Do you need me to transfer the call?

276
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:09,820
No need.

277
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,300
I just wanted to confirm.

278
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:12,860
Alright, thank you.

279
00:13:12,940 --> 00:13:13,340
Goodbye.

280
00:13:34,980 --> 00:13:35,820
Good evening.

281
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:37,380
You're back.

282
00:13:38,222 --> 00:13:40,222
Perfect timing,
I have something for you.

283
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:41,900
What is it?

284
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:48,780
What's this?

285
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:51,780
Out of the twenty,
you selected ten promising ones.

286
00:13:52,060 --> 00:13:53,980
But since I haven't
confirmed or signed off yet,

287
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,340
this list

288
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:57,580
can't be shared with
others in the company for now.

289
00:13:57,980 --> 00:13:59,020
I haven't finalized it yet.

290
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:00,220
I know.

291
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:02,250
And these two lists are different.

292
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:03,266
These ten and those ten,

293
00:14:03,311 --> 00:14:05,340
together make up
the twenty from the selection pool.

294
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,020
So,

295
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:07,540
this is a test list.

296
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:09,844
If someone in the company,
out of curiosity,

297
00:14:09,888 --> 00:14:10,820
asks you for the list,

298
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:12,900
like Mantou or Fragile,

299
00:14:13,155 --> 00:14:14,422
then give it to them.

300
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:16,540
But you must clearly tell them

301
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:17,660
not to pass it on.

302
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:21,020
Of course, besides those two,

303
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,100
there may also be

304
00:14:22,100 --> 00:14:23,460
a third or fourth person asking.

305
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:24,740
Handle it the same way.

306
00:14:25,060 --> 00:14:26,210
From the twenty,

307
00:14:26,210 --> 00:14:28,180
randomly give them a list of ten.

308
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:29,220
But

309
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,780
you must make sure

310
00:14:31,340 --> 00:14:33,420
each combination is different.

311
00:14:33,860 --> 00:14:35,060
And you need to keep track

312
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:37,220
of which set went to whom.

313
00:14:38,260 --> 00:14:40,860
So you're trying to find out
who leaked the list?

314
00:14:40,860 --> 00:14:42,244
Whoever leaks it is the insider.

315
00:14:42,580 --> 00:14:44,460
Zhao Lanxin loves
poaching new authors, right?

316
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:46,140
So let her keep digging.

317
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:49,140
Anyone who comes to ask me about it

318
00:14:49,140 --> 00:14:50,500
is already suspicious.

319
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:52,980
But we don't have evidence,

320
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:56,180
so the ones asking

321
00:14:56,180 --> 00:14:57,620
might just be curious

322
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:59,460
or have other reasons.

323
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:02,100
That's why we need this test.

324
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:05,860
I'm a bit nervous.

325
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,420
Everyone at the company

326
00:15:07,420 --> 00:15:08,460
has been really nice to me.

327
00:15:08,511 --> 00:15:10,644
Whoever it turns out to be,
it'll be hard to take.

328
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:14,866
Personal relationships and work
are two different things.

329
00:15:16,222 --> 00:15:17,622
You've gained weight lately.

330
00:15:18,311 --> 00:15:20,511
What kind of takeout
have you been eating?

331
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:23,420
Hello?

332
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:25,220
Suicide?

333
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,100
Miss Zhou, I'm really sorry

334
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:30,733
for causing you both so much trouble.

335
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:32,300
Why are you all here?

336
00:15:33,311 --> 00:15:35,100
She came looking for you and Zhangzhu.

337
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:36,355
I said a few words to her.

338
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:38,380
Then, I asked Mr. Cai to take her home.

339
00:15:38,533 --> 00:15:39,780
I didn't expect that on the way,

340
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,333
she'd try to jump out of the car.

341
00:15:43,780 --> 00:15:44,540
Jump out?

342
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:45,940
Is she seriously hurt?

343
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,060
She's fine.

344
00:15:47,288 --> 00:15:48,580
She was about to open the door,

345
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:50,044
and I pulled over immediately.

346
00:15:50,266 --> 00:15:51,666
There's no danger to her life.

347
00:15:52,066 --> 00:15:53,444
The police have already come.

348
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:54,930
I accompanied Zhou Mei and Mr. Cai

349
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:56,460
to explain the situation.

350
00:15:56,577 --> 00:15:58,666
There are surveillance
cameras outside your building

351
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,340
that recorded their entire conversation.

352
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,060
It proves there was

353
00:16:02,260 --> 00:16:03,810
no physical contact

354
00:16:03,810 --> 00:16:05,266
or serious conflict between them.

355
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:06,260
I'm really sorry.

356
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:08,100
I thought she came looking for Zhangzhu,

357
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:09,860
since she knows
Zhangzhu lives with Ms. Lin.

358
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:11,700
But I didn't expect

359
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:14,340
she thought Ms. Lin and I...

360
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:18,340
So, I'm really sorry.

361
00:16:20,733 --> 00:16:22,555
Fortunately, Lawyer Bei was with you.

362
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:24,020
If anything had escalated,

363
00:16:24,180 --> 00:16:25,260
he'd know how to handle it.

364
00:16:25,977 --> 00:16:27,911
I happened to have
dinner with Zhou Mei tonight

365
00:16:27,955 --> 00:16:29,044
to discuss some matters.

366
00:16:29,380 --> 00:16:29,780
Look,

367
00:16:30,620 --> 00:16:32,060
this has disrupted their meal

368
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:34,940
and their evening.

369
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:36,340
I'm really sorry.

370
00:16:36,460 --> 00:16:37,460
Sorry, truly sorry.

371
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:44,220
It was work, just work.

372
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,740
Nothing to do with anything else.

373
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:49,060
I asked Lawyer Bei to take
a look at a contract for me.

374
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:51,000
He didn't charge a consultation fee,

375
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:51,900
so I

376
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:53,260
treated him to dinner

377
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:54,380
as a thank-you.

378
00:16:57,460 --> 00:16:59,540
Then, how about I treat
everyone to a meal tomorrow?

379
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:00,220
Somewhere nearby.

380
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:03,380
Why are you being so abrupt?

381
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:05,820
Ms. Lin, Lawyer Bei, and Zhou Mei

382
00:17:05,820 --> 00:17:06,700
are all very busy.

383
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:08,620
Why don't you ask if they're free first?

384
00:17:08,780 --> 00:17:10,860
Well, if tomorrow doesn't work,
then another day.

385
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:12,180
Whenever you're free,

386
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,260
I'll treat you.

387
00:17:13,466 --> 00:17:15,340
To be honest,
I have a selfish reason too.

388
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:17,140
The police are coming again tomorrow,

389
00:17:17,311 --> 00:17:19,644
and with Lawyer Bei there,
I can ask a few more questions.

390
00:17:21,488 --> 00:17:23,380
Don't worry.
I'll definitely be there tomorrow.

391
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:32,780
If you're free,

392
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:33,860
you're welcome to join.

393
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:35,100
Really?

394
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:36,420
That's great.

395
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,100
Thank you.

396
00:17:38,100 --> 00:17:39,177
Thank you, Lawyer Bei.

397
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:40,140
Well,

398
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:43,460
Miss Zhou,
your male friend is really decent.

399
00:17:43,860 --> 00:17:44,260
Really.

400
00:17:44,340 --> 00:17:45,540
You're lucky, Miss Zhou.

401
00:17:47,660 --> 00:17:49,060
Zhou Mei and I will head back first.

402
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:51,260
And Lawyer Bei

403
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:52,980
should go home to his wife and child.

404
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:06,980
Then...

405
00:18:08,580 --> 00:18:09,300
It's settled

406
00:18:10,140 --> 00:18:10,940
for tomorrow.

407
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,500
See you tomorrow.

408
00:18:13,620 --> 00:18:13,980
Alright.

409
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:14,500
Okay.

410
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:14,980
Alright.

411
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:17,180
Should I

412
00:18:18,460 --> 00:18:19,500
send you three back?

413
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:21,420
No need. It's not on the way.

414
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:22,660
We'll take a taxi.

415
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:25,540
Then, how about

416
00:18:25,900 --> 00:18:26,660
I send you back?

417
00:18:28,100 --> 00:18:28,820
Alright, thanks.

418
00:18:43,700 --> 00:18:44,740
So when Zhangzhu's dad

419
00:18:44,740 --> 00:18:46,020
called you just now,

420
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:48,620
you were already
having dinner with Lawyer Bei?

421
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:50,460
We had just sat down.

422
00:18:50,533 --> 00:18:51,933
Hadn't even started eating yet.

423
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:53,844
Ms. Mei, weren't you supposed to
have dinner

424
00:18:53,866 --> 00:18:54,955
with Lawyer Bei tomorrow?

425
00:18:55,066 --> 00:18:56,577
He had something come up tomorrow,

426
00:18:56,622 --> 00:18:57,755
so we moved it to today.

427
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:01,540
He just agreed to have a meal

428
00:19:01,540 --> 00:19:03,111
with Zhangzhu's dad tomorrow.

429
00:19:03,511 --> 00:19:05,466
How could he suddenly
have plans tomorrow?

430
00:19:05,711 --> 00:19:08,377
It's not the first time
he's changed plans at the last minute.

431
00:19:11,300 --> 00:19:12,380
He just has a lot going on.

432
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:20,860
He's teaching you

433
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:23,700
to fall in line.

434
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:36,380
Alright.

435
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,820
My dad has already
booked a place for tomorrow.

436
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,260
Didn't you all agree

437
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:47,940
to go together?

438
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,140
Send me the address.

439
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:51,933
Mei and I will head over tomorrow.

440
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:54,300
Okay.

441
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:04,780
Working this late again?

442
00:20:05,700 --> 00:20:07,220
Your boss is exploiting you.

443
00:20:07,288 --> 00:20:08,444
You could report her.

444
00:20:08,888 --> 00:20:10,330
I've got a session with Zhang Yousen,

445
00:20:10,330 --> 00:20:11,540
doing some online Q&A.

446
00:20:13,333 --> 00:20:14,940
He's more reliable than AI, right?

447
00:20:15,888 --> 00:20:17,488
I'm the one answering his questions.

448
00:20:17,755 --> 00:20:19,410
What questions could
you answer for him?

449
00:20:19,410 --> 00:20:20,820
What kind of man Zhou Mei likes.

450
00:20:21,711 --> 00:20:23,780
Whether Zhou Mei
actually wants to get married.

451
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:24,780
Why Zhou Mei broke up

452
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:26,300
with each of her exes.

453
00:20:26,420 --> 00:20:28,619
Why Zhou Mei still
doesn't have a steady boyfriend.

454
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:29,822
Whether Zhou Mei has even

455
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:32,220
the slightest interest in Zhang Yousen.

456
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:35,340
Can you even answer
any of those yourself?

457
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:38,060
No.

458
00:20:38,288 --> 00:20:40,133
That's why we're
discussing it as a group.

459
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:43,980
He's online.

460
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:48,540
(Zhang Yousen
invites you to a voice call)

461
00:20:48,740 --> 00:20:49,380
Are you home yet?

462
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:51,060
Is Zhou Mei back?

463
00:20:52,420 --> 00:20:52,980
Not yet.

464
00:20:53,780 --> 00:20:55,300
She probably went out with her friend.

465
00:20:56,044 --> 00:20:57,420
Then let's talk a bit longer.

466
00:20:57,740 --> 00:20:58,980
Maybe she'll be back soon.

467
00:21:00,180 --> 00:21:01,380
I want to ask you something.

468
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:04,740
It's also something I
want to tell Zhou Mei.

469
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:05,700
Go ahead.

470
00:21:06,111 --> 00:21:07,660
Our company is opening a new branch.

471
00:21:07,844 --> 00:21:09,111
It's the Southwest branch.

472
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:10,940
They need someone to go,

473
00:21:11,533 --> 00:21:13,311
but once you go, it's for two years.

474
00:21:14,088 --> 00:21:16,511
After that,
there's a chance to become a partner.

475
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:18,940
I'm thinking of applying,

476
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:20,940
but I'm worried

477
00:21:22,022 --> 00:21:24,133
that if I go,
I won't see her for a long time.

478
00:21:27,466 --> 00:21:29,180
I originally planned
to have Zhang Yousen

479
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:31,180
help Zhangzhu
manage new author contracts.

480
00:21:31,511 --> 00:21:33,600
Didn't expect
the conversation to go this way.

481
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:35,820
If you can motivate a young person

482
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:37,900
to work hard because of this,

483
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:40,420
then you've done
at least one good thing,

484
00:21:41,740 --> 00:21:42,860
enough to offset

485
00:21:43,580 --> 00:21:45,540
a tiny fraction of
your many wrongdoings.

486
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:52,740
But speaking of which,

487
00:21:52,940 --> 00:21:54,580
Zhangzhu works pretty hard.

488
00:21:54,777 --> 00:21:56,444
You've found a good assistant this time.

489
00:21:56,820 --> 00:21:58,620
She leans a bit too much
toward outsiders.

490
00:21:58,888 --> 00:21:59,822
What do you mean?

491
00:22:00,180 --> 00:22:01,580
She's good at screening new authors,

492
00:22:02,577 --> 00:22:04,620
but that's because
she found a great helper.

493
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:05,980
Experienced,

494
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:07,180
fast at reading,

495
00:22:07,580 --> 00:22:09,420
and most importantly, fits my taste.

496
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:13,820
Who?

497
00:22:15,100 --> 00:22:15,740
He Han?

498
00:22:17,060 --> 00:22:18,340
They think I don't know.

499
00:22:22,860 --> 00:22:24,340
Don't tell me He Han

500
00:22:24,377 --> 00:22:26,133
is trying to get back with you again?

501
00:22:34,580 --> 00:22:35,980
This time is different.

502
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:40,380
We've been apart for so long,

503
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:42,980
so there's no going back.

504
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:49,140
I don't think he sees it that way.

505
00:22:57,420 --> 00:22:58,820
Author Night invitation.

506
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:00,540
Will you go with me?

507
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:03,460
This year's Author of the Year

508
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:04,980
will most likely be Gu Yan.

509
00:23:05,177 --> 00:23:06,377
If you're not winning anything,

510
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:07,060
why would I go?

511
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:08,540
I'd rather spend that time

512
00:23:09,140 --> 00:23:10,660
reading a novel.

513
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,044
Then I won't go either.

514
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:13,540
You have to go.

515
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:16,140
If you don't, you'll look petty.

516
00:23:16,700 --> 00:23:17,780
Not only do you have to go,

517
00:23:17,900 --> 00:23:19,940
but you also need to
manage your expressions.

518
00:23:21,260 --> 00:23:23,420
When Gu Yan goes on
stage to accept the award,

519
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:25,020
you need to show your congratulations

520
00:23:25,020 --> 00:23:27,180
to both Gu Yan and Lin Zhanqiao.

521
00:23:31,100 --> 00:23:31,620
See you.

522
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:45,580
(Dingqi 2024 Annual Author Night)

523
00:23:49,460 --> 00:23:50,060
Hey,

524
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:53,140
every time you meet Lawyer Bei,

525
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:54,660
do you really need two hours

526
00:23:54,660 --> 00:23:55,620
to get ready like this?

527
00:23:55,900 --> 00:23:56,511
Of course.

528
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:00,155
And you're going to
dinner dressed like that?

529
00:24:00,780 --> 00:24:01,555
What's wrong?

530
00:24:01,822 --> 00:24:04,044
Aren't you going to
change into something nicer?

531
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:06,260
At least show some respect
for the people there.

532
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:08,060
I'll show it with my attitude.

533
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:09,740
That's enough.

534
00:24:11,460 --> 00:24:12,060
You know,

535
00:24:12,700 --> 00:24:14,780
this dinner
is actually quite special to me.

536
00:24:15,420 --> 00:24:15,980
Why?

537
00:24:17,340 --> 00:24:18,940
This is the first time Lawyer Bei and I

538
00:24:19,066 --> 00:24:20,666
are having a meal with my friends.

539
00:24:21,060 --> 00:24:22,500
Before, he would never do this.

540
00:24:23,244 --> 00:24:24,311
You get what I mean?

541
00:24:24,340 --> 00:24:24,820
Not really.

542
00:24:26,244 --> 00:24:28,977
If you put it that way,
I kind of don't want to go anymore.

543
00:24:29,220 --> 00:24:30,420
I originally thought

544
00:24:30,444 --> 00:24:32,355
this was just Cai Dezhang's
thank-you dinner.

545
00:24:33,660 --> 00:24:35,180
It is a thank-you dinner,

546
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:37,620
but to me, it means something different.

547
00:24:38,380 --> 00:24:39,500
If I didn't tell you,

548
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:40,500
you wouldn't know.

549
00:24:41,620 --> 00:24:42,620
But now you do.

550
00:24:45,020 --> 00:24:46,580
So in reality, you're having an affair.

551
00:24:47,180 --> 00:24:48,220
Cai Dezhang and Zhangzhu

552
00:24:48,220 --> 00:24:49,700
are just your cover.

553
00:24:50,100 --> 00:24:51,580
Don't put it so harshly.

554
00:24:51,844 --> 00:24:54,133
This is something private
between Lawyer Bei and me.

555
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,020
Zhangzhu is calling.

556
00:24:59,660 --> 00:25:00,020
Hello?

557
00:25:00,300 --> 00:25:01,260
Are you on your way?

558
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,711
I'll get there a bit earlier.

559
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:04,780
Lawyer Bei asked to add one more seat.

560
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:06,180
His wife will be joining us.

561
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:18,700
Alright, I got it.

562
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:19,620
Okay.

563
00:25:19,860 --> 00:25:20,500
See you later.

564
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:22,260
See you.

565
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:32,460
Lawyer Bei said he's bringing his wife.

566
00:25:36,980 --> 00:25:37,420
Why?

567
00:25:38,111 --> 00:25:39,600
Did she insist on coming?

568
00:25:42,066 --> 00:25:43,666
Why didn't he say this earlier?

569
00:25:43,977 --> 00:25:45,422
What do you think his purpose is?

570
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:48,620
First,

571
00:25:49,333 --> 00:25:51,844
he doesn't want others to
question your relationship.

572
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:53,140
Second,

573
00:25:53,980 --> 00:25:55,420
he wants you to know your place.

574
00:25:56,700 --> 00:25:57,140
Third,

575
00:25:57,666 --> 00:25:58,860
he wants you to understand

576
00:25:58,980 --> 00:26:00,060
that on important occasions,

577
00:26:00,140 --> 00:26:01,940
he will show up with his wife.

578
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:05,622
So you get used to it and accept it.

579
00:26:12,044 --> 00:26:13,333
So are you still going?

580
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:16,580
Of course.

581
00:26:17,288 --> 00:26:18,311
Why wouldn't I?

582
00:26:28,180 --> 00:26:28,860
Don't worry.

583
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:31,580
I've never wanted to ruin his marriage.

584
00:26:32,060 --> 00:26:33,140
He knows that.

585
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:36,020
If I were you, I wouldn't go.

586
00:26:36,488 --> 00:26:38,266
Even if you go, you won't be happy.

587
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:39,666
And if I don't go, I will be?

588
00:26:41,220 --> 00:26:41,780
I promise,

589
00:26:42,133 --> 00:26:43,580
I'll act more sincerely than anyone

590
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:45,060
in wishing his marriage well.

591
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:46,220
Let's go.

592
00:27:20,980 --> 00:27:22,260
I'm in construction.

593
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:23,580
You could say I'm a careful man.

594
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:25,288
But compared to Lawyer Bei,

595
00:27:25,300 --> 00:27:26,100
I'm nothing.

596
00:27:26,980 --> 00:27:29,220
His mind is so meticulous
that nothing slips through.

597
00:27:29,300 --> 00:27:30,780
What you think of and what you don't,

598
00:27:31,060 --> 00:27:32,466
he's already thought it through.

599
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:33,660
You flatter me.

600
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:35,340
Part of our job

601
00:27:35,340 --> 00:27:37,155
is to prevent problems
before they happen.

602
00:27:37,260 --> 00:27:37,780
Mrs. Bei,

603
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:38,977
having a husband like him

604
00:27:39,140 --> 00:27:39,740
is impressive.

605
00:27:40,700 --> 00:27:41,420
You wouldn't know.

606
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:42,780
Our friends all say

607
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:44,260
he's incredibly sharp,

608
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:46,500
born to be a lawyer.

609
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:47,020
Right?

610
00:27:47,660 --> 00:27:48,860
Ms. Lin and Zhou Mei are here.

611
00:27:48,860 --> 00:27:50,222
- I'll go greet them.
- Alright.

612
00:27:50,900 --> 00:27:51,420
Ms. Lin,

613
00:27:53,820 --> 00:27:54,660
they're all here.

614
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:01,400
Hello, Ms. Lin.

615
00:28:02,088 --> 00:28:02,900
Hello, Miss Zhou.

616
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:03,460
Mr. Cai.

617
00:28:05,740 --> 00:28:06,660
You must be Mrs. Bei.

618
00:28:09,540 --> 00:28:10,888
Let me introduce everyone.

619
00:28:11,300 --> 00:28:12,260
This is Zhou Mei.

620
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:13,820
This is Lin Zhanqiao.

621
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:16,260
Zhanqiao is Zhangzhu's boss.

622
00:28:17,980 --> 00:28:18,900
This is my wife.

623
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:21,540
Hello, Miss Lin.

624
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:22,844
Hello, Miss Zhou.

625
00:28:23,500 --> 00:28:25,740
Young women these days
are truly accomplished.

626
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:29,540
Come, have a seat.
Don't just stand there.

627
00:28:29,540 --> 00:28:30,220
Sit.

628
00:28:31,511 --> 00:28:32,244
Ms. Lin, here.

629
00:28:34,500 --> 00:28:34,860
Ms. Lin.

630
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:35,740
Thank you.

631
00:28:41,340 --> 00:28:41,740
Thank you.

632
00:28:52,460 --> 00:28:53,540
Excuse me, pour the wine.

633
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:57,220
It's not easy to get everyone together.

634
00:28:58,180 --> 00:28:58,500
Come.

635
00:28:58,940 --> 00:28:59,660
Napkin here.

636
00:29:00,444 --> 00:29:01,180
Thank you, Dear.

637
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:03,940
Lawyer Bei, have some wine.

638
00:29:04,740 --> 00:29:05,140
Of course.

639
00:29:05,820 --> 00:29:06,260
Thank you.

640
00:29:06,333 --> 00:29:08,066
This wine was recommended by a friend.

641
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:09,300
Give it a try.

642
00:29:11,622 --> 00:29:13,100
Please add another set of utensils.

643
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:14,222
There will be one more person.

644
00:29:14,266 --> 00:29:15,311
Alright, just a moment.

645
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,260
Who did you invite?

646
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:19,580
My boyfriend.

647
00:29:23,380 --> 00:29:25,380
Mei,
since when have you had a boyfriend?

648
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:26,620
I've always had one.

649
00:29:27,340 --> 00:29:28,420
You just didn't know.

650
00:29:33,888 --> 00:29:35,620
With how beautiful you are, Miss Zhou,

651
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:37,580
there must be countless men chasing you.

652
00:29:37,820 --> 00:29:38,420
Zhanqiao,

653
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:40,700
have you met Zhou Mei's boyfriend?

654
00:29:46,380 --> 00:29:46,940
She has.

655
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:49,260
Yes.

656
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:50,620
Who is it?

657
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:55,220
Does your boyfriend drink?

658
00:29:57,222 --> 00:29:58,260
He can drink a little.

659
00:29:59,340 --> 00:30:00,700
Here, pour that glass.

660
00:30:01,340 --> 00:30:02,780
And add one more serving,

661
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:04,288
same as the others.

662
00:30:04,820 --> 00:30:05,260
Thank you.

663
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:15,460
Mrs. Bei, are you working now

664
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:17,580
or helping Lawyer Bei

665
00:30:17,580 --> 00:30:19,100
with things at home and outside?

666
00:30:20,380 --> 00:30:22,220
We sent our son abroad last year,

667
00:30:22,780 --> 00:30:24,340
so now I've

668
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:25,466
started working again.

669
00:30:25,540 --> 00:30:25,860
Yes.

670
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,940
What kind of business
does your company do?

671
00:30:29,820 --> 00:30:30,740
Just some

672
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:32,420
product packaging design and the like.

673
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:34,500
I just run a small studio.

674
00:30:34,820 --> 00:30:36,700
More of a personal interest.

675
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:38,380
Thanks to my husband.

676
00:30:38,620 --> 00:30:40,380
Everything is arranged perfectly for me.

677
00:30:41,020 --> 00:30:42,660
I really just got pushed into it.

678
00:30:42,911 --> 00:30:43,955
Give it a try.

679
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:47,220
See, when choosing a boyfriend,

680
00:30:47,377 --> 00:30:49,220
you should find someone like Lawyer Bei.

681
00:30:50,220 --> 00:30:51,620
A truly capable man

682
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:53,180
can take care of everything,

683
00:30:53,180 --> 00:30:54,700
both work and family.

684
00:30:55,060 --> 00:30:55,860
I'm not like that.

685
00:30:56,060 --> 00:30:57,180
If I take care of one side,

686
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:58,340
I can't handle the other.

687
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:00,340
Mei,

688
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:02,100
what does your boyfriend do?

689
00:31:03,900 --> 00:31:04,940
He's also a lawyer.

690
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:16,700
What a coincidence.

691
00:31:17,111 --> 00:31:19,220
Then he should have
a good talk with Lawyer Bei,

692
00:31:19,220 --> 00:31:20,377
and learn a thing or two.

693
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,260
It's a rare opportunity,

694
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,244
isn't it, Lawyer Bei?

695
00:31:23,511 --> 00:31:24,220
You flatter me.

696
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:25,820
We can learn from each other.

697
00:31:27,820 --> 00:31:28,420
Actually,

698
00:31:29,266 --> 00:31:30,820
he's already learning from Lawyer Bei.

699
00:31:36,620 --> 00:31:37,100
Really?

700
00:31:37,244 --> 00:31:37,980
What a coincidence.

701
00:31:38,300 --> 00:31:39,300
Is he a colleague

702
00:31:39,420 --> 00:31:40,660
of my husband's firm?

703
00:31:42,260 --> 00:31:42,700
Dear,

704
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:44,740
you never mentioned him.

705
00:31:48,340 --> 00:31:49,380
Zhang Yousen?

706
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,088
Over here.

707
00:31:55,460 --> 00:31:55,780
Come.

708
00:32:03,820 --> 00:32:04,380
Lawyer Bei.

709
00:32:05,020 --> 00:32:05,460
Mrs. Bei.

710
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:07,340
Zhangzhu.

711
00:32:07,860 --> 00:32:08,260
Ms. Lin.

712
00:32:08,822 --> 00:32:09,666
Hello, Ms. Lin.

713
00:32:10,660 --> 00:32:11,460
And this is?

714
00:32:11,933 --> 00:32:12,733
Have a seat.

715
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,660
This is Zhangzhu's father.

716
00:32:16,260 --> 00:32:16,980
Hello, Mr. Cai.

717
00:32:17,088 --> 00:32:18,533
- Hello.
- I'm Zhang Yousen.

718
00:32:18,740 --> 00:32:20,660
What a fine young man, well-presented.

719
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:22,780
Miss Zhou,

720
00:32:23,066 --> 00:32:24,500
your boyfriend is quite young.

721
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:30,140
So your boyfriend is Zhang Yousen.

722
00:32:30,980 --> 00:32:32,140
What a small world.

723
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:35,020
Yousen is Lawyer Bei's assistant.

724
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:36,980
Miss Zhou,

725
00:32:37,500 --> 00:32:39,220
did you meet Zhang Yousen first

726
00:32:39,580 --> 00:32:41,060
or Lawyer Bei first?

727
00:32:42,420 --> 00:32:44,940
Lawyer Bei introduced me to Zhou Mei.

728
00:32:45,380 --> 00:32:46,220
For work reasons.

729
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:47,700
Zhang Yousen,

730
00:32:47,911 --> 00:32:50,533
you really had me fooled,
keeping this from me all this time.

731
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:52,460
When did you two get together?

732
00:32:52,460 --> 00:32:53,980
I had no idea.

733
00:32:54,288 --> 00:32:56,977
I really thought you were secretly
in love with Zhou Mei all along.

734
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,260
I'm quite surprised, too.

735
00:33:01,420 --> 00:33:02,400
We've only been together

736
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:03,180
for a few days.

737
00:33:05,620 --> 00:33:06,180
Miss Zhou,

738
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,660
before this,

739
00:33:07,777 --> 00:33:09,020
were you single all along?

740
00:33:11,866 --> 00:33:12,977
You could say that.

741
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:17,780
Miss Lin, you're single too, right?

742
00:33:20,733 --> 00:33:22,822
I don't really have
time for a relationship.

743
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:25,580
You women are all so capable.

744
00:33:27,288 --> 00:33:28,490
If you're going to find someone,

745
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:30,288
it should be someone
who can take care of you.

746
00:33:36,780 --> 00:33:37,780
Not having a boyfriend

747
00:33:38,444 --> 00:33:40,155
doesn't mean there's no one you like.

748
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:57,488
You have someone you like, Ms. Lin?

749
00:34:00,180 --> 00:34:02,020
There's a lot to take in today.

750
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:05,400
Come. Let's serve the dishes.

751
00:34:11,180 --> 00:34:11,580
Thank you.

752
00:34:13,620 --> 00:34:13,940
Come.

753
00:34:14,555 --> 00:34:15,533
Let me make a toast.

754
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:16,740
Today,

755
00:34:17,288 --> 00:34:18,180
thank you, everyone.

756
00:34:18,620 --> 00:34:21,340
Especially Lawyer Bei and Ms. Lin,

757
00:34:21,620 --> 00:34:23,460
for taking care of Zhangzhu
during this time.

758
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:25,340
Thank you all. Let's have a drink.

759
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,755
Why am I the only one
finishing my glass?

760
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:43,800
Here, I'll drink with you.

761
00:34:46,380 --> 00:34:46,900
Zhang Yousen,

762
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:49,380
why is your face so red?

763
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,780
Is it from the alcohol,

764
00:34:50,780 --> 00:34:52,020
or because of Zhou Mei?

765
00:34:53,340 --> 00:34:54,060
I just feel

766
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:56,140
so lucky.

767
00:35:02,311 --> 00:35:03,380
Lawyer Bei, thank you

768
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:04,955
for introducing Zhou Mei to me.

769
00:35:05,860 --> 00:35:06,700
Thank you, Mrs. Bei.

770
00:35:07,111 --> 00:35:08,333
Thank you, everyone.

771
00:35:18,820 --> 00:35:19,300
Thank you,

772
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:20,780
Zhou Mei.

773
00:35:49,340 --> 00:35:51,300
So sweet.

774
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:54,500
Oh my.

775
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,540
Miss Zhou. Miss Lin.

776
00:36:06,622 --> 00:36:08,000
Let's add each other on WeChat.

777
00:36:08,133 --> 00:36:10,244
Come over to our place when you're free.

778
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:14,980
Sure.

779
00:36:28,333 --> 00:36:30,355
We'll grab a taxi across the street.

780
00:36:31,860 --> 00:36:32,180
Bye.

781
00:36:32,180 --> 00:36:32,900
Let's go, Miss Zhou.

782
00:36:32,940 --> 00:36:33,340
Bye.

783
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:34,511
- Take care.
- Bye.

784
00:36:36,911 --> 00:36:38,066
Lawyer Bei, Mrs. Bei,

785
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:39,088
you too, take care.

786
00:36:40,020 --> 00:36:41,180
Thank you for coming today.

787
00:36:41,333 --> 00:36:42,577
If you ever need anything

788
00:36:42,660 --> 00:36:44,100
related to real estate,

789
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:45,140
just let me know.

790
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,800
Thank you for your kind invitation.

791
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,320
I'm sure we'll be troubling you again.

792
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:48,800
Definitely.

793
00:36:48,900 --> 00:36:49,260
Alright.

794
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:49,940
Take care.

795
00:36:50,066 --> 00:36:50,460
Goodbye.

796
00:36:50,460 --> 00:36:50,780
Alright.

797
00:36:50,860 --> 00:36:51,180
Bye.

798
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:51,920
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

799
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:52,420
Bye.

800
00:36:52,740 --> 00:36:53,140
Bye.

801
00:37:42,060 --> 00:37:42,800
The car's here.

802
00:37:44,020 --> 00:37:44,340
Okay.

803
00:37:45,300 --> 00:37:45,820
Then...

804
00:37:46,660 --> 00:37:47,380
I'll get going.

805
00:37:47,644 --> 00:37:50,260
My girlfriend is still in the hospital,
getting discharged tomorrow.

806
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:51,700
Miss Qian

807
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:52,420
is fine now?

808
00:37:52,733 --> 00:37:53,460
She's alright.

809
00:37:53,533 --> 00:37:54,580
It wasn't a serious fall.

810
00:37:54,580 --> 00:37:55,460
Just a check-up.

811
00:38:00,620 --> 00:38:02,980
Zhangzhu, stay a few more days
at Ms. Lin's place.

812
00:38:03,420 --> 00:38:05,088
I'll come find you once I'm done here.

813
00:38:05,288 --> 00:38:07,133
No need to come find me. I'm doing fine.

814
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:08,000
That won't do.

815
00:38:08,844 --> 00:38:10,222
How about I give you a ride?

816
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:12,300
No need. It's easy to get a taxi.

817
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:14,580
Alright, we're off.

818
00:38:17,660 --> 00:38:18,300
Take care.

819
00:38:29,020 --> 00:38:33,500
(Zhanqiao: Clean up your posts,
and remove what needs removing.)

820
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:38,820
So why?

821
00:38:40,044 --> 00:38:41,300
Why did you suddenly say yes?

822
00:38:41,660 --> 00:38:42,780
And in front of everyone.

823
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:43,940
I still can't believe it.

824
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:47,820
Just on a whim.

825
00:38:48,940 --> 00:38:50,140
Sometimes, you don't

826
00:38:50,140 --> 00:38:51,644
need a reason for things like this.

827
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:52,900
Zhou Mei,

828
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:54,420
thank you.

829
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,100
Really.

830
00:38:56,940 --> 00:38:58,420
Even if it was just on a whim.

831
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:03,340
I should be the one thanking you.

832
00:39:31,220 --> 00:39:32,940
Leave the door unlocked for Mei.

833
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:35,180
I thought she and Zhang Yousen...

834
00:39:36,460 --> 00:39:37,620
She'll be back later.

835
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:43,020
Do you want some wontons?

836
00:39:44,740 --> 00:39:45,220
Now?

837
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:47,210
Didn't we just eat?

838
00:39:47,210 --> 00:39:48,820
That didn't really count as eating.

839
00:39:49,511 --> 00:39:51,400
If you don't want any,
just watch me eat.

840
00:39:53,220 --> 00:39:55,860
So we're going for wontons now?

841
00:39:56,111 --> 00:39:56,977
Of course.

842
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:58,380
What did you think,

843
00:39:59,060 --> 00:40:00,580
that I was walking you home?

844
00:40:01,780 --> 00:40:02,340
No.

845
00:40:02,820 --> 00:40:03,820
I'm just a bit nervous.

846
00:40:04,260 --> 00:40:06,060
I share an apartment with friends.

847
00:40:10,977 --> 00:40:13,140
Add this, and that's the authentic
Shanghai flavor.

848
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:16,540
Do you come here often?

849
00:40:17,622 --> 00:40:19,266
Been eating here for over 20 years.

850
00:40:21,155 --> 00:40:22,711
This place has been around that long?

851
00:40:25,940 --> 00:40:27,340
I lived upstairs when I was a kid.

852
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:29,777
So your mom used
to bring you here a lot?

853
00:40:32,140 --> 00:40:33,260
Acting like a wild kid, huh?

854
00:40:33,711 --> 00:40:34,644
Come on, let's go.

855
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:35,822
Come home with me.

856
00:40:39,700 --> 00:40:40,940
(Buying all this useless stuff!)

857
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:42,155
(Everything in my house...)

858
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:43,700
(Yes, it's all yours.)

859
00:40:43,700 --> 00:40:44,580
(Year 2004)
Touch them, and I'll fight you!

860
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:45,300
I'll touch them, so what?

861
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:46,340
Are you even human?

862
00:40:46,980 --> 00:40:47,900
I'm not human?

863
00:40:47,900 --> 00:40:48,780
You're a beast!

864
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:49,540
I'm a beast?

865
00:40:49,540 --> 00:40:51,155
Even a beast has more dignity than you.

866
00:40:51,420 --> 00:40:52,410
Then you married a beast.

867
00:40:52,410 --> 00:40:53,740
- Shut up!
- Who do you think you are?

868
00:40:53,740 --> 00:40:54,860
You're no better.

869
00:40:54,860 --> 00:40:56,390
- I'm telling you.
- Get out.

870
00:40:57,500 --> 00:40:58,540
Don't ever come back.

871
00:40:59,540 --> 00:41:00,570
Come in and sit.

872
00:41:00,570 --> 00:41:01,911
I will make you a bowl of wontons.

873
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:03,700
(Arguing again?)

874
00:41:03,700 --> 00:41:05,620
♪My heart is beating still♪

875
00:41:06,740 --> 00:41:09,660
♪Sometimes I feel alone♪

876
00:41:10,311 --> 00:41:11,488
What are you thinking about?

877
00:41:11,933 --> 00:41:13,100
Thinking about your mom?

878
00:41:13,100 --> 00:41:15,444
She used to bring you here
to sit in this spot, right?

879
00:41:16,140 --> 00:41:16,540
Yeah.

880
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:19,500
Was she

881
00:41:19,500 --> 00:41:20,733
as strict with you back then?

882
00:41:21,860 --> 00:41:24,420
♪That lies inside my head♪

883
00:41:24,420 --> 00:41:24,980
Not really.

884
00:41:27,580 --> 00:41:29,020
So you miss this place

885
00:41:30,300 --> 00:41:31,380
because it holds

886
00:41:32,020 --> 00:41:33,500
your childhood memories, right?

887
00:41:39,220 --> 00:41:39,980
♪I guess I guess♪

888
00:41:39,980 --> 00:41:45,300
♪It's rising from my silence♪

889
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:49,300
♪I'm nothing but the one♪

890
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:53,420
♪Who paints the blue sky♪

891
00:41:54,500 --> 00:41:56,100
♪With all of my tears♪

892
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,380
♪And past pain♪

893
00:41:58,844 --> 00:42:00,755
I really wish I had met you back then.

894
00:42:03,220 --> 00:42:06,540
♪Please stay with me♪

895
00:42:07,340 --> 00:42:08,660
You weren't even born yet.

896
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:10,260
Then I wish I were a few years older,

897
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:11,580
so when

898
00:42:11,580 --> 00:42:13,060
your mom brought you here,

899
00:42:13,644 --> 00:42:15,533
I could pretend to come eat here, too.

900
00:42:15,977 --> 00:42:16,780
When I was little,

901
00:42:17,140 --> 00:42:18,420
I was smart and well-behaved.

902
00:42:19,100 --> 00:42:21,100
Your mom would definitely have liked me.

903
00:42:22,260 --> 00:42:23,020
And I'd tell her,

904
00:42:23,866 --> 00:42:25,022
Mrs. Zhou, don't worry.

905
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:26,900
I'll protect her forever.

906
00:42:27,020 --> 00:42:31,340
♪Don't bind my soul♪

907
00:42:37,500 --> 00:42:38,180
Thank you.

908
00:42:40,155 --> 00:42:41,460
What do you usually like to eat?

909
00:42:44,020 --> 00:42:44,700
I like noodles.

910
00:42:46,380 --> 00:42:47,700
Then, next time,

911
00:42:47,700 --> 00:42:49,200
take me to eat your favorite noodles.

912
00:42:49,540 --> 00:42:50,060
Better not.

913
00:42:50,740 --> 00:42:52,140
You might not like what I like.

914
00:42:52,444 --> 00:42:53,420
Then you'd be unhappy.

915
00:42:53,900 --> 00:42:55,100
Who's happy all the time?

916
00:43:05,921 --> 00:43:07,041
(I've been thinking.)

917
00:43:08,321 --> 00:43:11,601
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

918
00:43:12,361 --> 00:43:19,691
(is probably different.)

919
00:43:20,691 --> 00:43:22,441
♪If the sky♪

920
00:43:22,951 --> 00:43:24,351
♪And the sea♪

921
00:43:24,891 --> 00:43:26,601
♪Turned upside down♪

922
00:43:28,161 --> 00:43:30,091
♪If a swimming fish♪

923
00:43:30,491 --> 00:43:33,881
♪Fell in love with a flying bird♪

924
00:43:35,651 --> 00:43:37,621
♪If back then♪

925
00:43:37,981 --> 00:43:42,391
♪We had never let go♪

926
00:43:42,991 --> 00:43:49,271
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

927
00:43:50,391 --> 00:43:52,541
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

928
00:43:52,541 --> 00:43:54,411
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

929
00:43:54,591 --> 00:43:57,031
♪And found our way back whole♪

930
00:43:57,871 --> 00:44:00,041
♪So let this surging love♪

931
00:44:00,041 --> 00:44:04,471
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

932
00:44:05,371 --> 00:44:07,551
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain♪

933
00:44:07,551 --> 00:44:08,641
♪That's alright♪

934
00:44:09,181 --> 00:44:09,931
♪If we're buried♪

935
00:44:09,931 --> 00:44:12,631
♪By passing years all the better♪

936
00:44:12,891 --> 00:44:15,071
♪At least we still can keep♪

937
00:44:15,251 --> 00:44:19,671
♪This one eternal photograph♪

938
00:44:35,431 --> 00:44:37,721
♪We're on misaligned tracks♪

939
00:44:37,721 --> 00:44:39,481
♪Running in opposite ways♪

940
00:44:39,601 --> 00:44:42,071
♪Searching all along the way♪

941
00:44:42,871 --> 00:44:45,031
♪For the fire of our younger hearts♪

942
00:44:45,221 --> 00:44:50,131
♪And the beauty lost in time♪

943
00:44:50,131 --> 00:44:53,651
♪This time don't lose each other again♪

944
00:44:53,891 --> 00:44:54,861
♪Only after loss♪

945
00:44:54,861 --> 00:44:57,491
♪Do we learn what truly matters most♪

946
00:44:57,901 --> 00:45:00,261
♪In another time and space♪

947
00:45:00,261 --> 00:45:01,821
♪We'll stay and walk together♪

948
00:45:01,821 --> 00:45:04,651
♪Till we grow old♪

949
00:45:05,611 --> 00:45:07,901
♪But still the sky will never♪

950
00:45:07,901 --> 00:45:10,571
♪Turn with the sea♪

951
00:45:13,091 --> 00:45:15,501
♪But still a swimming fish won't♪

952
00:45:15,501 --> 00:45:20,711
♪Fall in love with a flying bird♪

953
00:45:31,260 --> 00:45:31,820
Someone there?

954
00:45:33,660 --> 00:45:35,420
If you like pretty girls,

955
00:45:35,444 --> 00:45:36,777
then go ahead and pursue them.

956
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:37,780
But don't think

957
00:45:37,780 --> 00:45:39,260
dating a few girls can provoke me.

958
00:45:39,980 --> 00:45:41,060
I don't care at all.

959
00:45:41,420 --> 00:45:43,020
The one who laughs last laughs best.

960
00:45:43,420 --> 00:45:45,300
When I received this award back then,

961
00:45:45,700 --> 00:45:47,500
the one by my side supporting me

962
00:45:47,820 --> 00:45:48,980
was my best partner,

963
00:45:49,420 --> 00:45:50,100
Lin Zhanqiao.

964
00:45:50,533 --> 00:45:52,740
Even though this year
I'm not here to receive an award,

965
00:45:53,260 --> 00:45:54,460
the one beside me

966
00:45:54,860 --> 00:45:55,580
is still her.
